Pag. 194. Now all that Truth that is in any created Being, is by participation and derivation from this first Understanding (that is, from the Divine Understanding quatenus Exhibitive) and Fountain of Intellectual Light. That is, according to the Platonick Dialect, of those steady, unalterable and eternal Idea's (
                        〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                     ) of the natures and respects of things represented there in the Divine Understanding Exhibitive in their Objective Existence; In conformity to which the Truth in all created things and Understandings doth necessarily consist.
